high_descs: Turn around and walk straight then make a left near the wine bottle on the counter.
Pick up the wine bottle on the counter.
Turn back around then left to face the fridge. Walk towards the fridge.
Place the bottle on the top shelf in the fridge and close the door. Take the wine bottle back out and shut the door.
Turn to the right and make a quick right and walk towards the trash can.
Place the wine bottle in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Place the wine bottle in the fridge to put it in the trash can.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the kitchen
Pick the bottle of wine up
Carry the bottle of wine to the fridge
Grab the bottle of wine out of the fridge
Carry the bottle of wine to the trash can and throw it away
anns.task_desc: Was to throw the bottle of wine in the trash

high_descs: Turn and go to the counter by the toaster.
Pick up the bottle of wine.
Take the bottle to the fridge across the room.
Chill the bottle of wine in the fridge.
Take the chilled bottle across the kitchen to the recycle bin.
Throw the chilled bottle in the recycle bin.
anns.task_desc: Throw a cold wine bottle in the recycle bin.
